lead_paragraph: Triple Formula One world champion Lewis Hamilton won the Hungarian Grand Prix on Sunday to seize the championship lead from team mate Nico Rosberg for the first time this season.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton Wins in Hungary to Take Overall Lead
